title: Kill Or Be Killed
lastfmSummary: “Kill or Be Killed“ is a song by British rock band Muse. It was released on July 21, 2022 as the fourth single ahead of their ninth studio album “Will of the People“, having already debuted in live format during festival shows of their Will of the People World Tour. Borrowing its styles from metal bands such as Limp Bizkit, Slipknot, and Korn, and given its resemblence to Rage Against the Machine, “Kill or Be Killed” is a heavier reminiscence and mixture of Muse’s old-fashioned heavy tracks.
